    "However, there is a key distinction that needs to be made.",
    "Traditional KMSs categorize \"data\" as basic facts, \"information\" as processed and contextualized data, and \"knowledge\" as insights drawn from human experience and judgment.",
    "In contrast, GenAI compresses the information layer and creates knowledge directly by processing very large volumes of data.",
    "2 In a sense, while humans curate content in regular KMSs, GenAI uses algorithms for this task.",
    "Despite this management activities within organizations."
